'''Heidi Specogna''' (yavutse 5 Mutarama 1959) ni umukinnyi wa firime wo mu [[Ubusuwisi|Busuwisi]] . <ref>https://www.tvtime.com/en/actor/47553</ref> Yagize uruhare muri sinema yo muri [[Amerika]] yepfo no muri [[Afrika]] akora firime zizwi cyane, ''Das kurze Leben des José Antonio Gutierrez'', ''Cahier africain'' na ''Tupamaros'' .<ref>https://www.vatmh.org/en/grant-recipient-details/grant/400-heidi-specogna.html</ref> <ref>https://www.adk.de/de/presse/pressemitteilungen.htm?we_objectID=60191</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 5 Mutarama 1959 i Biel / Bienne, mu [[Busuwisi]]<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0817458/</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Yize mu ishuri ry’itangazamakuru i Zurich hanyuma akora nk'umunyamakuru mu bitangazamakuru bitandukanye byo mu [[Budage]] [[Ubusuwisi|n'Ubusuwisi]]. Nyuma yize mu Ishuri rya Filime na Televiziyo mu [[Budage]] i Berlin kuva 1982 kugeza 1988. Amaze kurangiza muri iryo shuri, yabaye umwarimu muri Film Academy Baden-Württemberg ku ma firime ya documentaire kuva 2003. Mu 1985, filime ye ngufi ya ''Traces'' yatsindiye igihembo cya Bern. <ref name="swissfilms">https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/film_search/filmdetails/-/id_person/1173435339A44D93AAB9A97CF5B88B9A </ref> <ref>http://www.famafilm.ch/filme/wachs-und-gold/bio-filmografie-heidi-specogna/</ref>

Yibanze cyane kuri sinema yo muri Amerika y'Epfo na [[Afurika]] kubera gukina amashusho cyane cyane binyuze mu nzu ye bwite yashinzwe mu 1990. Mu 1991, yakinnye bwa mbere hamwe na documentaire ''Tania la Guerillera'' ivuga ku barwanyi bo muri [[Boliviya]] ' Tamara Bunke '. Mu 1993, yakoze filime ''Rosa'' ivuga ku bikorwa bitemewe n’umukoresha wa radiyo kuri Rote Kapelle . Hanyuma mu 1996 yakinnye nka ''Tupamaros'', umutwe w'inyeshyamba kuva [[Irigwe|Uruguay]], muri documentaire y'izina rimwe.<ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/286889/</ref> <ref name="swissfilms">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/film_search/filmdetails/-/id_person/1173435339A44D93AAB9A97CF5B88B9A "Heidi Specogna Biography"]. swissfilms<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2011 yakoze documentaire ya ''Carte Blanche'' yibanda kuri [[Repubulika ya Santara Afurika|Repubulika ya Centrafrique]] . Filime ye ''Ubuzima Bugufi bwa José Antonio Gutierrez'' yatsindiye igihembo cya Film yo mu [[Busuwisi]] 2007 kubera documentaire nziza ndetse nigihembo cya Adolf Grimme . Hanyuma filime ''Carte Blanche'' yahawe igihembo cya filime nziza y’ururimi rw’ikidage i Duisburg mu 2011 nyuma iza guhabwa igihembo cy’itangazamakuru Gatolika. Filime ''Goal hunter's ship'' bwahawe igihembo cyabacamanza bagize urubyiruko muri Leipzig naho 'inkuru yumukobwa' yise ''Esther und die Geister'' yahawe igihembo cyuburenganzira bw’ikidage. Muri 2017, filime ye ''Cahier Africain'' ishingiye kuri Repubulika ya Centrafrique yibasiwe n’ibibazo, yakiriye igihembo cy’amafirime cy’Ubudage Lola, ndetse n’igihembo cy’amafirime yo mu [[Busuwisi]] kubera filime nziza mu bihembo by’Ubudage by’Uburenganzira bwa Muntu, ndetse na  the Silver Dove in Leipzig muri 2018 igihembo cya Adolf Grimme. <ref>https://www.filmakademie.de/de/studium/studienangebote/dokumentarfilm/lehrende/?tx_fabwinstructors_instructors%5Binstructor%5D=40&tx_fabwinstructors_instructors%5Bce_uid%5D=10375&tx_fabwinstructors_instructors%5Baction%5D=show&tx_fabwinstructors_instructors%5Bcontroller%5D=Instructor&cHash=57b7d2844731e8f927dcc9f9320f2ca5</ref> <ref>https://www.grimme-preis.de/archiv/2018/preistraeger/p/d/heidi-specogna-1/</ref><ref>https://muse.jhu.edu/article/235347/summary</ref>

Muri 2019, Specogna yahawe igihembo cya Konrad Wolf muri Academy yubuhanzi. Muri 2020, iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Solothurn ryeguriye gahunda idasanzwe “Rencontre” kuri Specogna kubera kwibuka uruhare rwe muri sinema nyafurika.<ref>https://www.filmportal.de/nachrichten/konrad-wolf-preis-2019-geht-an-heidi-specogna</ref> <ref>https://www.solothurnerzeitung.ch/solothurn/stadt-solothurn/heidi-specogna-ist-ehrengast-der-rencontre-an-den-solothurner-filmtagen-2020-135861957</ref>

